Analytics for Mortgage enables loan officers and managers to drive increased mortgage sales by helping prioritize the customer leads and mortgage applications to focus on. Process loans faster by highlighting the mortgage applications that have the highest value, applications that have been open the longest, and applications that are missing documents.

NOTE: Analytics for Mortgage is included with CRM Analytics for Financial Services, which is available at an extra charge for customers with Financial Services Cloud Basic or Standard licenses and the FSCAnalyticsPlus license. See Deploy CRM Analytics for Financial Services for complete deployment instructions.
